<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5778853>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Mustura taretensis, sp. nov., holotype, female, MUMF 18007, 52.0 mm SL; a. lateral, b. dorsal and c. ventral views. India: Manipur: Tengnoupal District: Taret River (Chindwin River drainage)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5778853/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5778855>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Lip structure of Mustura taretensis, sp. nov. (MUMF 18007, 52.0 mm SL)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5778855/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5778857>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Air bladder of a. Mustura taretensis, sp. nov. (MUMF 18017, 41.8 mm SL); b. M. dikrogensis (MUMF 11092, 36.6 mm SL)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5778857/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5778862>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Coiling pattern of intestine of Mustura taretensis, sp. nov. (MUMF 18016, 38.8 mm SL)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5778862/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5778864>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Lateral view of head of males of a. Mustura taretensis, sp. nov. (MUMF 18010, 45.9 mm SL); b. M. chindwinensis (MUMF 11077, 43.3 mm SL); c. M. dikrongensis (MUMF 11092, 36.6 mm SL); d. M. tigrina (MUMF 11051, 73.6 mm SL) and e. M. tuivaiensis (MUMF 5086, 40.9 mm SL), showing suborbital flap." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5778864/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5778866>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Pectoral fin of male of a. Mustura taretensis, sp. nov. (MUMF 18018, 50.5 mm SL); b. male of M. chindwinensis (MUMF 11074, 39.68 mm SL); c male of M. dikrongensis (MUMF 11092, 36.6 mm SL); d. male of M. tirgina (MUMF 11051, 73.6 mm SL); e. male of M. tuivaiensis (MUMF 5086, 40.9 mm SL), showing wider first branched rays and tubercles and f. female of M. taretensis, sp. nov. (MUMF 18011, 43.7 mm SL), showing unexpanded first branched ray." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5778866/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5778868>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Coloration of Mustura taretensis, sp. nov., paratypes: a. female, MUMF 18009, 46.6 mm SL, b. female, MUMF 18014, 40.1 mm SL." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5778868/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5778870>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Dorsum of head of Mustura taretensis, sp. nov., showing dark brown rhomboidal mark on nape a. holotype, female, MUMF 18007, 52.0 mm SL; b. paratype, female, MUMF 18009, 46.6 mm SL." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5778870/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5778872>
    dc:description "FIGURE 9. Map showing the type localities of Mustura species in the Chindwin-Irrawaddy River drainage: 1. Mustura celata, 2. M. chindwinensis, 3. M. prashadi, 4. M. shuensis, 5. M. tigrina, 6. M. yunnaniloides and 7. M. taretensis, sp. nov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5778872/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5778874>
    dc:description "FIGURE 10. Image showing habitat of Mustura taretensis, sp. nov., in Taret River, Manipur, India." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5778874/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

